#9- The Haunting 
The police think the son of a wealthy and influential Hawaiian family is responsible for a slew of murders in the U.S. Jim Phelps and his team get the mission to find the evidence that will prove his guilt...or innocence.

#11- The Greek 
Jim and his team must neutralizea greek tycoon who runs an international black market drug ring. 

#12- The Fortune 
A dictator seeks asylum in the United States after stealing all of his countrys funds.Now, the team must locate the money and steal it back.
